{"tid":842782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啊邊個邊個 個仔一出黎俾咁多家用啊！","createTime":"2018-09-30T15:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T20:43:49.000Z","uid":55340,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4beb37cd787d0473dc583c1576ca21dbd4382cf8","tid":842782,"uid":55340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"究竟班三姑六婆、師奶吹夠水未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日係到亂噏廿四，啊陳師奶個仔揾2萬俾1.8萬家用啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個仔呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班離地撚，係啊人地俾成份糧屋企，但係食屋企住屋企，咩都唔洗理，仲留左層樓俾佢添一<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔見佢地咁講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n俾家用仲要受氣，唔係要儲錢，一早想搬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4786c33af6f3ea5f9ef4091208098699d48b7d92","tid":842782,"uid":189943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:16:21.000Z","msg":"忍下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856279d14ace77dde889583998cc1349c599b278","tid":842782,"uid":14766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"畀9成家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百年一遇既孝子"},{"pid":"c82bc3236330ef429b8ae41d0a4617082cfc981b","tid":842782,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"班三姑六婆<br />\n咪好似連登仔人工吹水大會咁<br />\n吹得鬥勁"},{"pid":"75fc6de69ca5ea99616a5b366a62a4304c7bcbee","tid":842782,"uid":55340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c82bc3236330ef429b8ae41d0a4617082cfc981b","tid":842782,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:20:30.000Z","msg":"班三姑六婆<br />\n咪好似連登仔人工吹水大會咁<br />\n吹得鬥勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"啲老母會信到十足十，再一傳十 十傳百<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif